*Restoranu* je uvijek pun. (The restaurant is always full.)
Ona voli da ide u *restoranu*. (She loves to go to the restaurant.)
On je otišao u *restoranu*. (He went to the restaurant.)
Njegov najdraži *restoran* je u gradu. (His favorite restaurant is in the city.)
Njegov prijatelj je vlasnik *restorana*. (His friend is the owner of the restaurant.)
Ona često ide u *restoranu* sa prijateljima. (She often goes to the restaurant with friends.)